skills.name: Fist of Conviction
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Ice DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Ice DMG equal to 60% of Gepard's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Daunting Smite
skills.simple_desc: Deals Ice DMG to a single enemy, with a chance of Freezing them.
skills.desc:
Deals Ice DMG equal to 110% of Gepard's ATK to a single enemy, with a 65% base chance to Freeze the enemy for 1 turn(s).
While Frozen, the enemy cannot take action and will take Additional Ice DMG equal to 33% of Gepard's ATK at the beginning of each turn.

skills.name: Enduring Bulwark
skills.simple_desc: Provides a Shield to all allies.
skills.desc: Applies a Shield to all allies, absorbing DMG equal to 42% of Gepard's DEF plus 532 for 3 turn(s).

skills.name: Unyielding Will
skills.simple_desc: When struck by a killing blow, instead of being knocked down, immediately restores HP. This effect can only trigger 1 time per battle.
skills.desc: When struck with a killing blow, instead of becoming knocked down, Gepard's HP immediately restores to 27% of his Max HP. This effect can only trigger once per battle.

skills.name: Comradery
skills.simple_desc: After this character uses Technique, all allies gain a Shield at the start of the next battle.
skills.desc: After Gepard uses his Technique, when the next battle begins, a Shield will be applied to all allies, absorbing DMG equal to 24% of Gepard's DEF plus 150 for 2 turn(s).

light_cone.name: Day One of My New Life

relic_sets.name: Knight of Purity Palace
relic_sets.desc: Increases the max DMG that can be absorbed by the Shield created by the wearer by 20%.

relic_sets.name: Belobog of the Architects
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's DEF by 15%. When the wearer's Effect Hit Rate is 50% or higher, the wearer gains an extra 15% DEF.

skills.name: Dazzling Blades
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Wind DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to 50% of Sampo's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Ricochet Love
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Wind DMG to single enemy targets with 5 Bounces in total.
skills.desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to 42% of Sampo's ATK to a single enemy, and further deals DMG for 4 extra time(s), with each time dealing Wind DMG equal to 42% of Sampo's ATK to a random enemy.

skills.name: Surprise Present
skills.simple_desc: Deals Wind DMG to all enemies with a high chance to increase the DoT dealt to the targets.
skills.desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to 144% of Sampo's ATK to all enemies, with a 100% base chance to increase the targets' DoT taken by 27% for 2 turn(s).

skills.name: Windtorn Dagger
skills.simple_desc: After this character hits an enemy, there is a chance of inflicting Wind Shear on the target.
skills.desc:
Sampo's attacks have a 65% base chance to inflict Wind Shear for 3 turn(s).
Enemies inflicted with Wind Shear will take Wind DoT equal to 31% of Sampo's ATK at the beginning of each turn. Wind Shear can stack up to 5 time(s).

skills.name: Shining Bright
skills.simple_desc: Enemies in a set area are Blinded. When initiating battle against a Blinded enemy, there is a high chance to delay all enemies' actions.
skills.desc:
After Sampo uses his Technique, enemies in a set area are inflicted with Blind for 10 second(s). Blinded enemies cannot detect your team.
When initiating combat against a Blinded enemy, there is a 100% fixed chance to delay all enemies' action by 25%.

light_cone.name: Resolution Shines As Pearls of Sweat

relic_sets.name: Musketeer of Wild Wheat
relic_sets.desc: The wearer's SPD increases by 6% and Basic ATK DMG increases by 10%.

relic_sets.name: Sprightly Vonwacq
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's Energy Regeneration Rate by 5%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's action is Advanced Forward by 40% immediately upon entering battle.

skills.name: Midnight Tumult
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Lightning DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Lightning DMG equal to 50% of Kafka's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Caressing Moonlight
skills.simple_desc:
Deals Lightning DMG to a single enemy and minor Lightning DMG to adjacent targets.
If the main target currently has a DoT effect inflicted on it, the DoT deals DMG 1 extra time.
skills.desc:
Deals Lightning DMG equal to 140% of Kafka's ATK to a target enemy and Lightning DMG equal to 52% of Kafka's ATK to enemies adjacent to it.
If the target enemy is currently receiving DoT, all DoTs currently placed on that enemy immediately produce DMG equal to 71% of their original DMG.

skills.name: Twilight Trill
skills.simple_desc:
Deals minor Lightning DMG to all enemies, with a high chance of Shocking them.
If the enemies are currently Shocked, the Shock status deals DMG 1 extra time.
skills.desc:
Deals Lightning DMG equal to 72% of Kafka's ATK to all enemies, with a 100% base chance for enemies hit to become Shocked and immediately take DMG from their current Shock state, equal to 95% of its original DMG. Shock lasts for 2 turn(s).
While Shocked, enemies receive Lightning DoT equal to 224% of Kafka's ATK at the beginning of each turn.

skills.name: Gentle but Cruel
skills.simple_desc: After an ally uses Basic ATK on an enemy, Kafka immediately launches a follow-up attack and deals Lightning DMG with a high chance of inflicting Shock to that target. This effect can only be triggered 1 time per turn.
skills.desc: After an ally of Kafka's uses Basic ATK on an enemy target, Kafka immediately launches 1 follow-up attack and deals Lightning DMG equal to 103% of her ATK to that target, with a 100% base chance to inflict Shock equivalent to that applied by her Ultimate to the attacked enemy target, lasting for 2 turns. This effect can only be triggered 1 time per turn.

skills.name: Mercy Is Not Forgiveness
skills.simple_desc: Attacks all enemies within range. After entering battle, deals minor Lightning DMG to all enemies with a high chance of Shocking them.
skills.desc: Immediately attacks all enemies within a set range. After entering battle, deals Lightning DMG equal to 50% of Kafka's ATK to all enemies, with a 100% base chance to inflict Shock equivalent to that applied by her Ultimate on every enemy target for 2 turn(s).

relic_sets.name: Band of Sizzling Thunder
relic_sets.desc: When the wearer uses their Skill, increases the wearer's ATK by 20% for 1 turn(s).

relic_sets.name: Space Sealing Station
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's ATK increases by an extra 12%.

skills.name: Thwack
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to 80% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Sheathed Blade
skills.simple_desc: Deals Quantum DMG to a single enemy and increases SPD.
skills.desc: Increases Seele's SPD by 25% for 2 turn(s) and deals Quantum DMG equal to 192% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Butterfly Flurry
skills.simple_desc: Enters the buffed state and deals massive Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Seele enters the buffed state and deals Quantum DMG equal to 382% of her ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Resurgence
skills.desc:
Enters the buffed state upon defeating an enemy with Basic ATK, Skill, or Ultimate, and receives an extra turn. While in the buffed state, the DMG of Seele's attacks increases by 70% for 1 turn(s).
Enemies defeated in the extra turn provided by "Resurgence" will not trigger another "Resurgence."

skills.name: Phantom Illusion
skills.desc: After using her Technique, Seele gains Stealth for 20 second(s). While Stealth is active, Seele cannot be detected by enemies. And when entering battle by attacking enemies, Seele will immediately enter the buffed state.

relic_sets.name: Genius of Brilliant Stars
relic_sets.desc: When the wearer deals DMG to the target enemy, ignores 10% DEF. If the target enemy has Quantum Weakness, the wearer additionally ignores 10% DEF.

relic_sets.name: Space Sealing Station
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's ATK increases by an extra 12%.
